headline: Carrier to Present at Goldman Sachs 2025 Industrials and Materials Conference
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR) Chairman & CEO David Gitlin will speak at the Goldman Sachs Industrials and Materials Conference on Thursday, December 4, 2025, at 8:40 a.m. ET.
